---
title: Panko-Crusted Shrimp with Potato Wedges and Dilly Cucumber Salad
description: This crispy, flaky shrimp dish has an incredible lemony-panko coating. A side of potatoes frites and dilly, creamy cucumber salad make for the perfect pairing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1022_W22_CA_RF159182-1_MAIN_low-391211db.jpg
